data.description: This beautiful one-story home on an extra-large corner lot features a spacious open floor plan + many upgrades including, appliances, flooring, lighting, plantation shutters, surge protectors on AC and heating units, UV light on air handler eliminates allergens, irrigation system w/driplines on trees, full house gutters, and water conditioner with RO system. An elegant entry way leads to the open family room w/14’ Ceilings. Enjoy the Spacious Island Kitchen w/Pendant lighting abundance of cabinets and drawers for Pots and Pans. Large master bdrm w/upg carpet, master bath featuring dbl sinks, a glass shower, and his and her walk-in closets. Large Patio, 13x19, with off set for a grill. ADT security system including a doorbell has been installed. Remote controlled ceiling fan in one of the three bedrooms. One of two front bedrooms is currently being used as a study. Must see the full upgrade list. Make your appointment today.
